" <div class=\"graphic\">",
"  <div class=\"figure\" style=\"width: 524px\">",
"   <div class=\"ttl\">",
"    Cutaneous ulceration in rheumatoid vasculitis",
"   </div>",
"   <div class=\"cntnt\" style=\"width: 504px; height: 329px; background-image: url(data:image/jpeg;base64,);\">",
"   </div>",
"   <div class=\"lgnd\">",
"    The classic cutaneous finding of rheumatoid vasculitis is a medium-vessel inflammatory process associated with ulcerated lesions of the lower extremities.",
